:'''Galba:''' Phainon! Good timing. Have you seen Piso around?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504109002_28-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504109002_28-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Did Piso tick you off again?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109107-->
::'''Galba:''' You bet! His teacher came knocking, said the little rascal's been skipping class lately.
::'''Galba:''' I was about to have a real talk with him, but to my surprise, he vanished first thing this morning. Must've known what was coming and ran off early.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} He might be over by the granary...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109110-->
:::'''Galba:''' Got it. I'll go drag him back in a bit. Thanks for the heads-up.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504109113-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109113-->
:::'''Galba:''' *sigh* That little scamp... If only he were half as easy to deal with as you...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I haven't seen him today.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109112-->
:::'''Galba:''' No problem. I'll keep looking. Not heading into the woods today anyway... Hmph, he thinks he can outrun me?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504109113-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109113-->
