:{{DIcon|Talk}} About the upcoming trip...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109115-->
::'''Galba:''' You guys set a date to head out yet? I caught some fat rabbits the other day, and they're all cured and ready. Make sure you swing by to grab them before you leave.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I... I haven't made up my mind yet...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109117-->
:::'''Galba:''' No worries. I get it. Take your time. No need to rush it.
:::'''Galba:''' But if you had to ask... it's a big world out there. Worth seeing a bit of it. I've hunted all my life, but I bet the birds caught in my snares have seen more than I ever will.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504109121-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109121-->
:::'''Galba:''' If you ask me, I'd say young folks should go out there and see the world themselves. It's gotta be better than staying stuck here forever.
:::'''Galba:''' And when you get tired, just come home. The smoke in the village always rises earlier than Aquila.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It'll probably be soon.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504109120-->
